emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait, including members of lota Phi Lambda Sorority, from left: Lois Lee Dorsey, Councilman Paul F. Jones, Marion Jordon, Charles A. Carpenter, Phi Chapter president Jeanne Farrish, and Anne Penn, gathered at Greene Hearth to celebrate National Business Week
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 27, 1957, page A13, reads: "Iotas' Dinner - Members of Iota Phi Lambda Sorority gave a charming dinner at the Greene Hearthe, celebrating National Business Week of the group, and honoring Marion Jordon. Pictured are Mrs. Lois Lee Dorsey, Councilman Paul F. Jones, Mrs. Jordon, Charles A. Carpenter. the speaker; Phi Chapter president, Jeanne Farrish, and Anne Penn... - Harris Photo."
